This paper discusses decision-making under uncertainty, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also mentions expert-system design, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SI). The use of statistical properties of large samples suggests a connection to data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper discusses the practical applications of the proposed method, which could fall under software engineering (cs.SE).
